sources.description:
The Perfect Heist Unleashed A Nightmare | Wrong Place, Wrong Time - A daring crew of vigilantes hatches a high-stakes plan to swipe a staggering 14 billion dollars in laundered cash from a ruthless mob boss. But when betrayal strikes at the worst moment, they find themselves taking refuge in a desolate area with a mysterious family hiding a chilling secret. As darkness falls, they uncover the shocking truth: the patriarch is a creature of the night. Now, they must battle for their lives until the break of dawn!
2021.  Stars: Mike Markoff, Chase Garland, Bianca Stein, Timothy McKinney
